title: Santa's Boots [2 discs FLAC with art 2006]
description:
Santa's Boots is a wonderful collection of live performances,
 one delightful holiday track after another.
 It has professional sound quality in FLAC files.
 It's mostly Christmas music, with one Hannukah tune.
  
 This was put together with love, but not by me.
 The creator of this collection even made album art.
 Thanks to that person.  This is not for sale.
 Please pass it on. Listen to it with the ones you love.
 Happy Xmas.
